					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I should post this now even though It's missing decoding, but this is my idea for accommodating your encoding options.<br /><br />The header if used is encoded in 2 bytes:  YYYYYIII nnnnnnnn<br />n = number of blocks per interleave (0 means 256)<br />I = number of interleaves per segment minus 1<br />Y = number of segments (unimplemented)<br /><br />For the case of non interleaved pages, the first byte is then 0.</div>

					
